#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Basics</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Det grundlæggende</strong>"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Do you want to go further?</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Vil du tage det et skridt videre?</strong>"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Final word</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Afsluttende bemærkning</strong>"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>In such situation, feel free to experiment with this database and then to create a\n"
"            new one for your own usage.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Du er velkommen til at eksperimentere i sådanne situationer og\n"
"            oprette en ny til egen anvendelse.</strong>"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use case</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Brugsscenarie</strong>"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A good practice might be to keep those forecasts up to date for the coming months with\n"
"          your sales, so that the manufacturing team plans at best the production at all time\n"
"          accordingly!"
msgstr ""
"En god praksis er at holde disse prognoser opdateret for de kommende måneder "
"med\n"
"          dit salg, så produktionsholdet til enhver tid kan planlægge "
"produktionen mest effektivt og i overensstemmelse\n"
"          hermed!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add some Salt and Sugar to secure suppliers for longer on those sides."
msgstr ""
"Tilsæt lidt salt og sukker for at sikre leverandørernes engagement på disse "
"produkter."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"All Manufacturing Orders here are Ready to manufacture by default but you can play with\n"
"        the filters at top right of the screen to see them all."
msgstr ""
"Alle produktionsordrer er som standard klar til produktion, men du kan "
"bruge\n"
"        filtrene øverst til højre på skærmen for at se dem alle."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Also order the Mayonnaise so you can fill those buckets with sauce."
msgstr "Bestil også mayonnaise, så du kan fylde spandene med sauce."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As an Inventory Manager you need to make sure that the production team never runs out of\n"
"          supply!"
msgstr ""
"Som lagerchef er det dit ansvar at sørge for, at dit produktionsteam aldrig "
"løber tør for\n"
"          varer!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Between production and deliveries, by default, the product picking is "
"organized in FIFO."
msgstr ""
"Produktplukningen mellem produktion og levering følger som standard FIFO-"
"princippet."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_9
msgid "Bucket 5L"
msgstr "Spand, 5 l"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a few products, sale\n"
"      orders and more."
msgstr ""
"Når du uploader dette moduls demodata, bliver din database fyldt med nye "
"produkter,\n"
"      salgsordrer m.m."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click on one of the Ready orders to produce some Mayonnaise."
msgstr "Klik på én af de ordrer, der er klar, for at producere mayonnaise."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Close Production button at the end of the tile when done with all steps. Great\n"
"        you manufactured you first Mayonnaise batch!"
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen \"Luk produktion\" til sidst, når alle trin er fuldført. "
"Tillykke,\n"
"        du har produceret din første portion mayonnaise!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Confirm the Purchase Order when in agreement with your supplier."
msgstr "Bekræft indkøbsordren, når du og din leverandør er enige."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Confirm the order to close your deal."
msgstr "Bekræft ordren for at lukke aftalen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create an Invoice, send it to your customer and confirm it to get paid for "
"your hard work!"
msgstr ""
"Opret en faktura, send den til din kunde, og bekræft den for at få betaling "
"for dit hårde arbejde!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Define dates to plan those smaller orders along the corresponding period to smoothen the\n"
"        load and then proceed to the split.<br/>As a result, the initial order has been split into\n"
"        multiple smaller orders."
msgstr ""
"Planlæg datoer for de mindre ordrer over perioden for at lette\n"
"        belastningen, og fordel dem derefter.<br/>Den oprindelige ordre "
"opdeles på den måde i\n"
"        flere mindre ordrer."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Depending on your current stock level, an appropriate replenishment suggestion will be\n"
"        created for the final product and its components via the indirect demand, for instance here:\n"
"        the Bucket and the Dispenser, as well as the Mayonnaise down below."
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af dit lagerniveau oprettes en passende genopfyldningsordre\n"
"        for det færdige produkt og dets komponenter via den indirekte "
"anmodning, for eksempel her:\n"
"        spanden, dispenseren og mayonnaisen nedenfor."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Få mere at vide om Odoo i vores"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo offers to improve\n"
"      your experience."
msgstr ""
"Få indsigt i de grundlæggende funktioner i denne pakke, og udforsk de mange "
"muligheder, Odoo tilbyder, for at optimere\n"
"      din oplevelse."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_10
msgid "Dispenser 2.6L"
msgstr "Dispenser, 2,6 l"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Doing so, you have generated a new manufacturing order which is now visible for your\n"
"        operators."
msgstr ""
"Ved at gøre dette har du genereret en ny produktionsordre, som nu er synlig "
"for dine\n"
"        operatører."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Drag and drop manufacturing orders to spread evenly the load between Mayonnaise\n"
"        manufacturing and packaging into buckets and dispensers.<br/>You're all set for production!"
msgstr ""
"Træk og slip produktionsordrerne for at fordele belastningen jævnt mellem "
"mayonnaiseproduktionen\n"
"        og påfyldningen i spande og dispensere.<br/>Du er nu klar til at "
"sætte produktionen i gang!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Expiration Dates"
msgstr "Udløbsdatoer"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Fill in the form by creating or selecting a customer contact."
msgstr ""
"Udfyld formularen ved enten at oprette en ny kundekontakt eller vælge en "
"eksisterende."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"First, you might want to fill in your estimated Forecasted Demand for your finished\n"
"        products, in this case, Mayonnaise Bucket and Dispenser."
msgstr ""
"Først skal du indtaste den forventede efterspørgsel på dine fremstillede\n"
"        produkter – i dette tilfælde mayonnaise i spande og dispensere."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Follow as well the steps and close the production. Great, you now have some products to\n"
"        ship to delight customers."
msgstr ""
"Gennemfør trinene og afslut produktionen. Flot! Du har nu produkter\n"
"        klar til at blive sendt ud og begejstre dine kunder."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Follow the step from each operation to prepare your Mayonnaise batch."
msgstr ""
"Følg trinene i hver enkelt operation for at gennemføre produktionen af "
"mayonnaisen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Food distribution"
msgstr "Fødevaredistribution"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the <strong>Inventory App</strong>, keep track of produced lots and "
"expiration dates."
msgstr ""
"Hold styr på producerede partier og udløbsdatoer i "
"<strong>Lagerappen</strong>."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "From the <strong>Sales App</strong>, you can manage your orders."
msgstr "Du kan administrere dine ordrer i <strong>Salgsappen</strong>."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the Sale Order you confirmed, you can find a smart button to the associated delivery\n"
"        at the top."
msgstr ""
"I den bekræftede salgsordre finder du øverst en intelligent knap, som fører "
"dig direkte til den\n"
"        tilhørende levering."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Generate crystal clear quotations with the <strong>Sales App</strong>."
msgstr "Opret overskuelige tilbud i <strong>Salgsappen</strong>."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Having to follow up on supplies stock might be a repetitive task and you might forget...\n"
"        To\n"
"        help you with that, you can automate those orders. Filter on Auto Trigger in the left hand\n"
"        side tab to see already automated Replenishment Rules. Those rules will be triggered\n"
"        automatically to ensure you never run out of containers, that would be a shame to through\n"
"        away tasty Mayonnaise by lack of Buckets..."
msgstr ""
"Det kan være en gentagen opgave at holde styr på lagerbeholdningen, og det "
"er nemt at glemme ...\n"
"        For\n"
"        at gøre det lettere kan du automatisere bestillingerne. Filtrér "
"efter \"Automatisk udløser\" i venstre\n"
"        side for at se de allerede opsatte genopfyldningsregler. Disse "
"regler udløses\n"
"        automatisk, så du aldrig løber tør for beholdere. Det ville være "
"ærgerligt at skulle smide lækker mayonnaise ud,\n"
"        fordi der ikke er flere spande ..."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "Hej!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Here you can find some logistical data to optimize your deliveries."
msgstr ""
"Her finder du logistiske oplysninger, som kan hjælpe dig med at optimere "
"dine leverancer."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should Import demo\n"
"          data and try the Demo - Use Case (In the next Knowledge Article)"
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil gennemgå en praktisk rundvisning af dette modul, bør du "
"importere\n"
"          demodata og afprøve demoens brugsscenarie (som beskrevet i næste "
"artikel i Vidensdelingsappen)"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Introduce more capabilities from the <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Quality App</font>\n"
"        </strong> to meet the requirements\n"
"        from your market."
msgstr ""
"Udarbejd yderligere muligheder gennem <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kvalitetsappen</font>\n"
"          </strong>for at sikre, at kravene på dit\n"
"          marked bliver opfyldt."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoice your customers from the <strong>Invoicing App</strong>."
msgstr "Fakturér dine kunder via <strong>Faktureringsappen</strong>."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Let's now package the Mayonnaise now: Click on a Mayonnaise Bucket order to start the\n"
"        packaging."
msgstr ""
"Nu skal vi pakke mayonnaisen. Klik på en ordre for mayonnaisebøtter for at "
"starte\n"
"        pakningen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Leverage the<strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Barcode App</font>\n"
"        </strong> to manipulate products\n"
"        and serials without mistake."
msgstr ""
"Brug<strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Stregkodeappen</font>\n"
"        </strong> til at håndtere produkter\n"
"        og serienumre uden fejl."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage the purchase of raw materials from the <strong>Purchase App</strong>."
msgstr "Administrér indkøb af råvarer via <strong>Indkøbsappen</strong>."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated environment in <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting App</font>\n"
"        </strong>."
msgstr ""
"Administrér din bogføring nemmere end nogensinde i et fuldt integreret miljø "
"med <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Bogføringsappen</font>\n"
"        </strong>."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_3
msgid "Mayonnaise"
msgstr "Mayonnaise"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_12
msgid "Mayonnaise Bucket 5L"
msgstr "Mayonnaise, spand 5 l"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_13
msgid "Mayonnaise Dispenser 2.6L"
msgstr "Mayonnaise, dispenser 2,6 l"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_5
msgid "Mustard"
msgstr "Sennep"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Near its name, click the gear icon and select the split option.<br/>Define the Max Batch\n"
"        Size to correspond typically to the packaging of a Mayonnaise tank, 35 buckets in for\n"
"        example."
msgstr ""
"Klik på tandhjulsikonet ved siden af navnet, og vælg \"Opdel\".<br/>Angiv "
"den maksimale portionsstørrelse,\n"
"        som normalt svarer til emballagen på en mayonnaisetank,\n"
"        f.eks. 35 spande."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"No worries, simply increase the Replenishment for a product packaging Mayonnaise to grow\n"
"          the indirect demand of Mayonnaise just below your Actual Replenishment.<br/>This way, you\n"
"          make sure to package all you can, to deliver your customers according to your forecast,\n"
"          and have some buffer to start from next month."
msgstr ""
"Bare rolig, du skal blot øge genopfyldningsmængden for produktpakken "
"\"mayonnaise\" for at\n"
"          reducere den indirekte efterspørgsel til lige under din faktiske "
"genopfyldning.<br/>På den måde sikrer du,\n"
"          at du pakker alt, hvad du kan, leverer til dine kunder i henhold "
"til prognosen\n"
"          og samtidig har en buffer til næste måned."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now Send the Request For Quotation to your supplier if willing to iterate on price for\n"
"        example."
msgstr ""
"Send nu tilbudsanmodningen til din leverandør, f.eks. hvis du ønsker at "
"forhandle\n"
"        prisen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Now come back to the Sale Order which you can bill since delivered."
msgstr "Gå nu tilbage til salgsordren, som du kan fakturere efter leveringen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now come back to the list of manufacturing orders and open the calendar view from the top\n"
"        right hand side."
msgstr ""
"Gå nu tilbage til listen over produktionsordrer, og åbn kalendervisningen\n"
"        øverst til højre."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now let's see how spread the work load from the resulting manufacturing "
"orders."
msgstr ""
"Lad os nu se, hvordan arbejdsbyrden fordeles på de resulterende "
"produktionsordrer."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo giver dig ubegrænsede muligheder, såsom:"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this package. Feel free to\n"
"      add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Oversigten viser naturligvis kun de funktioner, der følger med pakken. Du "
"kan\n"
"      tilføje nye apps, redigere eller slette demodata og prøve dig frem!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On the Vinager Replenishment rule, hit the Order button. This creates a Purchase Order for\n"
"        this product according to the min and max input, which you can edit. Hit the Order button\n"
"        for\n"
"        Mustard while you're here to add those items to the recent Purchase Order."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen \"Bestil\" for genopfyldningsreglen for eddike. Dette "
"opretter en ordre\n"
"        på produktet i henhold til de indtastede minimums- og "
"maksimumsmængder, som du kan redigere. Mens du er her,\n"
"        kan du\n"
"        også klikke på »Bestil« for sennep for at tilføje disse varer til "
"den aktuelle ordre."

