msgstr ""
"Der er kun ét sidste skridt, før du kan bruge <strong>Faktureringsappen</"
"strong> til at fakturere: Levér!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open one of the finished product and navigate to the Inventory tab."
msgstr "Vælg et færdigt produkt, og åbn lagerfanen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Purchase App </strong>and the recently created Purchase "
"Order."
msgstr "Åbn <strong>Indkøbsappen</strong> og den nyligt oprettede ordre."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Master Production Schedule from the Planning menu.<br/>Don't panic, this will become\n"
"        your best buddy to optimize your production!"
msgstr ""
"Åbn produktionsplanen (MPS) i menuen \"Planlægning\".<br/>Ingen grund til "
"panik – denne plan bliver din bedste hjælper,\n"
"        når du skal optimere produktionen!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Mayonnaise Bucket for example since packaging such a quantity may not happen in\n"
"        one day."
msgstr ""
"Åbn f.eks. \"mayonnaise-spand\", da en så stor mængde muligvis ikke kan "
"pakkes på\n"
"        én dag."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Replenishment from Operations menu."
msgstr "Åbn genopfyldningen fra menuen \"Handlinger\"."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the list of manufacturing orders from the Operations menu."
msgstr "Åbn listen over produktionsordrer via menuen \"Handlinger\"."

