#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Producing efficiently is key for your business and doing so without running out of supplies\n"
"      is paramount. Let's open the <strong>Inventory App</strong> to see how to handle this aspect."
msgstr ""
"Effektiv produktion er afgørende for din virksomhed, og du må under ingen "
"omstændigheder løbe tør for\n"
"      lagerbeholdninger. Lad os åbne <strong>Lagerappen</strong> for at se, "
"hvordan du kan håndtere dette."

