"frequent segments!"
msgstr ""
"Spar tid ved at oprette tilbudsskabeloner til dine mest almindelige ordrer!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Select a quotation template to save time for an installation."
msgstr "Vælg en tilbudsskabelon for at spare tid ved installationen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Send your quotation for online signature."
msgstr "Send dit tilbud til online underskrivelse."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Setup your website for free and get leads passively with <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Website App </font>\n"
"        </strong>and <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM App</font>\n"
"        </strong>!"
msgstr ""
"Opret din hjemmeside gratis og få leads med <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Hjemmesideappen </font>\n"
"        </strong>og <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM-appen</font>\n"
"        </strong>!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Some plan, others produce... Open the <strong>Shop Floor App</strong> to manufacture\n"
"      products."
msgstr ""
"Nogle planlægger, andre producerer ... Åbn <strong>Værkstedsappen</strong> "
"for at starte\n"
"      produktionen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Some rules are defined to easily resupply ingredients and containers."
msgstr "Opret regler, så du nemt kan genbestille ingredienser og beholdere."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_7
msgid "Sugar"
msgstr "Sukker"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_2
msgid "Sunflower Oil"
msgstr "Solsikkeolie"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Take advantage of the power of <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Manufacturing App</font>\n"
"        </strong> with Manufacture To\n"
"        Order (MTO) capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Produktionsappen</font>\n"
"        </strong> med funktionen\n"
"        produktion efter ordre."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Bill of Material is accessible from the Manufacturing App Products menu."
msgstr "Styklisten kan hentes i Produktionsappen via menuen \"Produkter\"."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Dates section allows you to detail the expiration dates of your "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Brug afsnittet \"Datoangivelser\" til at indstille udløbsdatoer for dine "
"produkter."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Gantt view is available as well for even more intelligible planning from"
" version 19."
msgstr ""
"Gantt-visningen er tilgængelig fra version 19 og gør planlægningen endnu "
"mere overskuelig."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Mixing tank work center is configured with setup and cleanup time. Take advantage of\n"
"          this capability to optimize your operations!"
msgstr ""
"Arbejdsområdet \"Blandetanke\" er konfigureret med opsætnings- og "
"rengøringstider. Brug det\n"
"          til at optimere dine processer!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The products from the Replenishment Rules you triggered are here but not all products have\n"
"        Replenishment Rules at this stage. For some products or other suppliers you need, you can\n"
"        chose to add them manually to a Purchase Order and even create new Purchase Orders."
msgstr ""
"Produkterne fra de genopfyldningsregler, du har udløst, vises her, men ikke "
"alle produkter har\n"
"        genopfyldningsregler endnu. For nogle produkter eller leverandører "
"kan du\n"
"        manuelt tilføje dem til en indkøbsordre og endda oprette nye "
"indkøbsordrer."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"There is some stock of Buckets and Dispensers so no need to order some for the ongoing\n"
"        period.<br/>However, you need to order Mayonnaise Buckets to meet your forecast!"
msgstr ""
"Da der stadig er nogle spande og dispensere på lager, behøver du ikke "
"bestille nye i den løbende\n"
"        periode.<br/>Du skal dog bestille mayonnaisespande for at dække dit "
"aktuelle behov!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"There now is a smart button at the top of the Purchase Order to reach the associated\n"
"        delivery. Hit the Deliveries smart button to open the delivery."
msgstr ""
"Øverst i ordren finder du en intelligent knap, som giver adgang til den "
"tilhørende\n"
"        levering. Klik på knappen \"Leveringer\" for at åbne leveringen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"De er alle inkluderet i dit nuværende abonnement. Gå straks på opdagelse i "
"dem! 🙃"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This is great but you might be producing more Mayonnaise than you planned to"
" package..."
msgstr ""
"Fantastisk! Men måske producerer du mere mayonnaise, end du kan nå at pakke "
"..."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To save time and prevent mistake of typo in the Lot inputs, you might want to work with <strong>Barcode\n"
"          App</strong>!"
msgstr ""
"For at spare tid og undgå tastefejl ved indtastning af partinumre anbefaler "
"vi at bruge <strong>\n"
"          Stregkodeappen</strong>!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Maintenance App</font>\n"
"        </strong> to keep all your work\n"
"        centers up and running."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Vedligeholdelsesappen</font>\n"
"        </strong> til at holde alle dine\n"
"        arbejdscentre i gang."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>Manufacturing App</strong> to efficiently plan and execute production\n"
"        orders to meet customer demand."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>Produktionsappen</strong> til effektivt at planlægge og udføre "
"produktionsordrer,\n"
"        så du kan imødekomme kundernes efterspørgsel."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Validate the delivery to your customer to complete the job."
msgstr "Bekræft leveringen til kunden for at afslutte ordren."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model:product.template,name:food_distribution.product_template_4
msgid "Vinegar"
msgstr "Eddike"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When hovering the on the Order button for a product Replenishment, a cell is highlighted.\n"
"        Clicking this button orders the corresponding product for that period according to the\n"
"        Replenishment input.<br/>This creates a manufacturing order or a purchase order depending\n"
"        on the product configuration."
msgstr ""
"Når du holder musen over knappen \"Bestil\" for en produktopfyldning, "
"fremhæves en celle.\n"
"        Ved at klikke på knappen bestilles det tilsvarende produkt for "
"perioden i henhold til\n"
"        opfyldningsreglerne.<br/>Dette opretter enten en produktionsordre "
"eller en indkøbsordre, afhængigt af\n"
"        produktkonfigurationen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When the truck arrives and you add those to your stock, validate the delivery to update\n"
"        your stock levels. Don't forget to set the Lot reference in the details of the delivery\n"
"        lines. You're now ready to product Mayonnaise for some time!"
msgstr ""
"Når lastbilen ankommer, og du tilføjer varerne til lageret, skal du bekræfte "
"leveringen for at opdatere\n"
"        dine beholdninger. Husk at angive partireferencen i\n"
"        leveringslinjernes detaljer. Nu kan du producere mayonnaise i et "
"stykke tid!"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Whether you want to plan your production based on existing sales orders, or based on a\n"
"      forecast, you can use the master production schedule from the <strong>Manufacturing App</strong>\n"
"      ."
msgstr ""
"Uanset om du vil planlægge produktionen ud fra eksisterende salgsordrer "
"eller en\n"
"      prognose, kan du bruge produktionsplanen i <strong>Produktionsappen</"
"strong>\n"
"      ."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While you are using <strong>Inventory App</strong>, open the product catalog from the\n"
"        Products menu. This gives you a more comprehensive view of the different products you\n"
"        manipulate."
msgstr ""
"Åbn produktkataloget via menuen \"Produkter\", mens du bruger "
"<strong>Lagerappen</strong>\n"
"        . På den måde får du et mere komplet overblik over de produkter,\n"
"        du arbejder med."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Working on your pricing to optimize your margin? You leverage the \"Compute Price from\n"
"          BoM\" action available from the Product form or any Products list."
msgstr ""
"Arbejder du med prisfastsættelsen for at optimere din fortjeneste? Brug "
"funktionen \"Beregn pris fra\n"
"          stykliste\", som findes i produktformularen eller i enhver "
"produktliste."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are ready to sign your first customers? To do so, open the Sales App, create a new\n"
"        order and the customer."
msgstr ""
"Du er klar til at modtage dine første kunder. Åbn salgsappen, og opret en "
"ny\n"
"        ordre samt kunden."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilgå alle installerede apps i din Odoo-database direkte fra "
"hoveddashboardet."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now hurry to manufacture the needed products, deliver them prior sending the invoice\n"
"      to bill your customer."
msgstr ""
"Du kan nu producere de nødvendige produkter, levere dem og derefter sende\n"
"      fakturaen til kunden."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that the replenishment for the Mayonnaise comes as multiple of the batch\n"
"          size. You can adjust this editing the Mayonnaise Production Schedule from the pen icon\n"
"          near its name."
msgstr ""
"Du kan se, at genopfyldningsmængden for mayonnaise er et multiplum af "
"partistørrelsen\n"
"          .Du kan justere dette ved at redigere produktionsplanen for "
"mayonnaise via blyantikonet\n"
"          ved siden af navnet."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see the forecast clicking the chart icon. Down below, you can see that this is\n"
"          the\n"
"          outcome of all the planned Manufacturing Orders..."
msgstr ""
"Du kan se prognosen ved at klikke på diagramikonet. Nedenfor\n"
"          vises\n"
"          resultatet af alle planlagte produktionsordrer."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see you're about to get low on Vinegar and Mustard in the Forecast."
msgstr "Prognosen viser, at du snart løber tør for eddike og sennep."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can setup your Bill of Material to reflect on you production processes with or\n"
"          without steps, with embedded quality checks like in this example or after a production."
msgstr ""
"Du kan indstille din stykliste, så den afspejler dine produktionsprocesser – "
"med eller\n"
"          uden trin, med integreret kvalitetskontrol som i dette eksempel, "
"eller først efter produktionen."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt your Odoo\n"
"          setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Du har gennemført demoens brugsscenarie! Der findes millioner af måder at "
"tilpasse din Odoo-opsætning,\n"
"          så den passer til dine forretningsbehov."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries &gt; Upgrade\n"
"          your Bar &amp; Pub package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"Har du ikke importeret demodata endnu? Du kan stadig nå det. Gå til Apps &gt;"
" Brancher &gt; Opgradér\n"
"          din pakke til pubs og barer, og markér det relevante felt"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for <strong>Food distribution</strong> package. By doing so, we\n"
"      have installed a bunch of necessary apps to run your business efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Du har netop installeret Odoo-pakken til <strong>fødevareleverandører</"
"strong>. Samtidig er en række nødvendige apps installeret, så du kan drive "
"din virksomhed effektivt."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You might have tested this package with or without demo data. In any case, you may have\n"
"      written records in journals which are not deletable and which might be an issue for your\n"
"      traceability."
msgstr ""
"Du har muligvis testet denne pakke med eller uden demodata. Under alle "
"omstændigheder kan der\n"
"      være skriftlige optegnelser i journaler, som ikke kan slettes, og som "
"kan påvirke din\n"
"      sporbarhed."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You registered your first lot of Mayonnaise. Note that it is possible to change the lot\n"
"          number prefix from the product form, in the Inventory tab."
msgstr ""
"Du har registreret dit første parti mayonnaise. Du kan ændre præfikset for "
"partinummeret i\n"
"          produktformularen under fanen \"Lager\"."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of various flows you\n"
"      can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Med denne pakke i Odoo kan du gennemføre følgende flows\n"
"for hurtigt at få overblik over de forskellige processer."

